b0:["$","p",null,{"children":"Checks if a FORGE:STUB section has been modified by the user.  Compares the embedded hash (from the FORGE:STUB-HASH comment) against a freshly computed hash of the current inner content (with the hash comment itself stripped out). If the hashes diverge — meaning the user edited the content — or the hash comment was removed, the section is considered modified and should be preserved."}]
